data.description: Don't miss your opportunity to own this beautifully maintained home the heart of Deltona. Upon entering the home you're greeted by the formal living a dining areas which are great for entertaining. The generous sized kitchen includes plenty of counter and cabinet space with an amazing island and stainless-steel appliances. This home's open and spacious floor plan will definitely please any buyer. Schedule your private showing a see everything this home has to offer.
